@eggs_plode135 Dawnguard is a lot older than this patch. Usually you should grab all DLCs as well as the latest update- there's often a patch after a DLC is released to fix any bugs said DLC introduced.
Also note that if you want to use SKSE and most mods, you'll need the latest version.
